## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

###
## ─── Crafting Skills ───
###

### Get crafting skill levels
GET {{host}}/crafting/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Crafting Recipes ───
###

### Get all recipes (with canCraft status)
GET {{host}}/crafting/recipes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get blacksmithing recipes only
GET {{host}}/crafting/recipes?skill=blacksmithing
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get alchemy recipes only
GET {{host}}/crafting/recipes?skill=alchemy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get woodworking recipes only
GET {{host}}/crafting/recipes?skill=woodworking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Crafting Stations ───
###

### Get nearby crafting stations (must be at a station's town)
GET {{host}}/crafting/stations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Craft ───
###

### Craft a copper dagger (must be at Ironpeak Forge: 75,71)
POST {{host}}/crafting/craft
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "recipeId": "recipe-copper-dagger"
}

### Craft a health potion (must be at Mosswood Alchemy Lab: 81,48)
POST {{host}}/crafting/craft
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "recipeId": "recipe-health-potion"
}

### Craft a wooden shield (must be at Ferngate Woodshop: 29,25)
POST {{host}}/crafting/craft
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "recipeId": "recipe-wooden-shield"
}
